<P>
CONSUMER BILLS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Did anyone but me notice that of the 11 bills pending in Sacramento that would 
benefit beleaguered consumers (Part A, Aug. 31), not a single bill was 
sponsored by a Republican legislator? Just asking. 
</P>
<P>
WILLIAM S. SIMMONS 
</P>
