<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA090490-0010 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 271033 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 4, 1990, Tuesday, Southland Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 3; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
