APPEALS; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- SUITS; HISPANICS -- POLITICS; REAPPORTIONMENT -- 
LOS ANGELES COUNTY; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- ELECTIONS; FLORES, SARAH; O'BRIEN, 
GREGORY JR 
</P>
