ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: SAN CLEMENTE; 
</P>
<P>
GENERAL PLAN PANEL TO BE APPOINTED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
About 35 people have shown an interest in helping to revise the city's General 
Plan. 
</P>
<P>
The residents have taken out applications forms to join a 25-member citizens 
advisory committee that will review issues ranging from disaster preparedness 
to zoning laws. 
</P>
<P>
The deadline for submitting an application to City Hall is Wednesday at 5 p.m. 
</P>
</TEXT>
