past five seasons and hasn't won a league game in three years. The streak 
likely will continue this year but relief is in sight. The Tritons' sophomore 
team finished 5-5 last year, its best record in 10 seasons. The return of 
quarterback Dolan and the addition of Steve Castle as offensive coordinator 
will also improve the Tritons' four-points-per-game average in league last 
year. 
</P>
