He clips the speech processor, below, to his belt. LACY ATKINS / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Earplug; Photo, COLOR, (Orange County Edition) Casey Correia, 9, 
the first child in North America to receive a cochlear implant, now functions 
normally in hearing world . LACY ATKINS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
